licProfile?gid=akamekministud>akamek ministud</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 6<br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/22/02 5:57:05 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4706.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.steelwarrior.org/forum/p_sword.gif" align=absmiddle>  taunt weapons</span><hr size=1> Well I'm only level 41 (as of today btw).  I was using a Guard Captains Mallet primary and a Jarseth Trident secondary.  I was holding aggro pretty well but I got bored with that combo and I picked up a Venomous Axe of the Velium Brood which is 11/24 and 10ac <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :D --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/happy.gif ALT=":D"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  with an 85 dd proc, with a dex of 108 I average about 1-3 procs a fight and hold aggro better than I used to.  IMO it's a nice weapon and goes for about 600pp to 1k on prexus.  Yeah it's kinda slow but you may wanna give it a shot.  <br>
